title: Love Live! Sunshine!! Numazu Jimo Ai Festival
description:
is an Aqours live concert and fan meeting that took place in Numazu on the following days:
*August 11, 2022 with Shuka Saito, Aika Kobayashi and Ai Furihata
*August 13, 2022 with Rikako Aida, Nanaka Suwa, Arisa Komiya and Shuka Saito
*August 14, 2022 with Aika Kobayashi, Kanako Takatsuki, Aina Suzuki and Ai Furihata
